  - m_Id: 18106501590126600
    m_Localized: "This is the Derivative Work Game of the VTuber group 'Hololive'.\r\n\r\n\r\nTeam
      JEONGWON\r\n\r\n  Member -\r\n\r\n        game design, art by runinzem\r\n\r\n       
      rogrammed by a2no\r\n\r\n\r\nThose who helped us -\r\n\r\n  Play tester\r\n\r\n        
      Ali Play\r\n\r\n\r\n  SFX provider\r\n\r\n\r\n        pixabay        ViRiX               
      artisticdude\r\n\r\n        Skorpio        \u68EE\u7530\u4EA4\u4E00       
      faxcorp\r\n\r\n        jwiese        qubodup        dklon        \r\n\r\n       
      \r\n  BGM provider\r\n\r\n\r\n         (FIELD1)\r\n         \u30D5\u30A1\u30F3\u30BF\u30B8\u30FC03(\u6226\u3044\u306E\u30A2\u30FC\u30C1)
      - \u68EE\u7530\u4EA4\u4E00\r\n\r\n         (FIELD2)\r\n         \u30D5\u30A1\u30F3\u30BF\u30B8\u30FC04(\u6226\u6144\u306E\u65CB\u5F8B)
      - \u68EE\u7530\u4EA4\u4E00\r\n\r\n         (FIELD3)\r\n         \u30D5\u30A1\u30F3\u30BF\u30B8\u30FC05(Peaceful
      Place) - \u68EE\u7530\u4EA4\u4E00\r\n\r\n         (BOSS)\r\n         \u30D5\u30A1\u30F3\u30BF\u30B8\u30FC15(\u99C6\u3051\u629C\u3051\u308B\u6226\u5834\u306E\u5D50)
      - \u68EE\u7530\u4EA4\u4E00\r\n\r\n         (BOSSRAID)\r\n         \u30D5\u30A1\u30F3\u30BF\u30B8\u30FC11(bravery
      heart) - \u68EE\u7530\u4EA4\u4E00\r\n\r\n         (MAIN)\r\n          Lady
      of the 80's - Grand_Project"
